# Scenario: UserDriven-v1 with late spurious DeviceSetupProvisioningComplete after AccountSetup started.
# Reproduces regression from session e259c121-dc13-46d6-8e96-118f1da9845e (2026-04-22):
# ProvisioningStatusTracker fired DeviceSetupProvisioningComplete (payload
# deviceSetupResolved="unknown") AFTER AccountSetup was already in progress and
# DesktopArrived had been observed — but HelloResolved had NOT yet fired.
# Before the fix: the reducer completed the session to Stage=Completed unconditionally on
# DeviceSetupProvisioningComplete, short-circuiting Hello.
# After the fix: the handler detects AccountSetupEnteredUtc != null and treats the signal as
# informational only (stage unchanged, no completion effect). Completion happens on the
# subsequent HelloResolved via the Classic Hello+Desktop AND-gate.
# Expected terminal: Stage=Completed, Outcome=EnrollmentComplete, HelloOutcome=Success,
# last trigger = HelloResolved (NOT DeviceSetupProvisioningComplete).
# Plan: §6.1 regression fixture.
